Recommendations
Text is too small in OS_our-links, especially on mobile. Here's what I suggest:

Increase mobile minimum text size from 10px → 12px minimum (accessibility)
Align body text to 15-16px base instead of 14px on mobile
Increase description text from 12px → 14px minimum
Avoid 9px text - the handle text at 9px is too small; use 11px minimum
Increase line height for body content from 1.4 → 1.6 for better readability
